```

## Adding to package.json

Add these scripts to your `package.json`:

```json
{
  "scripts": {
    "seed": "node prisma/seed.js",
    "seed:{{featureName}}": "node prisma/seeding/{{featureName}}.seed.js"
  }
}
```

